
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>YelpCamp</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheet/home.css">
</head>
<body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
  
   <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
    
    <header class="mb-auto">
      <h3 class="float-start mb-0">YelpCamp</h3>
      <div>
        <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-end ms-auto">
          <a href="#" class="nav-link active" aria-current="page">Home</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/campgrounds">Campgrounds</a>
          <% if(!currentUser) { %>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
          <% } else { %>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
          <% } %>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="px-3">
      <h1 class="">YelpCamp</h1>
      <p class="lead">Welcome to YelpCamp! <br> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque maximus aliquam lacinia. Donec arcu nisl, posuere eget iaculis ac, lobortis at 
        tellus. Praesent sit amet nibh arcu. Proin varius, arcu sed tristique eleifend, neque elit porttitor sem, a sollicitudin felis
        </p>
      <a href="/campgrounds" class="btn-secondary btn btn-lg  font-weight-bold bg-white">View Campgrounds</a>
    </main>
    <footer class="mt-autho text-white-50">
      <p>&copy; YelpCamp 2024</p>
    </footer>
  
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>




